OL,3,CGPs to be trained to recognise
OL,4,Csymptoms of endometriosis earlier
OL,6,FGPs in Wales will be trained to
OL,7,Frecognise symptoms of endometriosis
OL,8,Fearlier, in a bid to improve diagnosis.
OL,10,FThe introduction of a specialist
OL,11,Ftraining programme comes six months
OL,12,Fafter the Welsh Government launched
OL,13,Fits Women's Health Plan for Wales. It
OL,14,Fis aimed at improving women's
OL,15,Fexperiences of healthcare across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,FEndometriosis is a chronic condition
OL,19,Fthat causes debilitating pain and can
OL,20,Fstart when women begin their period.
