OL,3,CGPs to be trained to recognise
OL,4,Csymptoms of endometriosis earlier
OL,6,FOne in ten women lives with the
OL,7,Fcondition, but the wait in Wales to
OL,8,Fget a diagnosis is longer than
OL,9,Fanywhere else in the UK and can take
OL,10,Fup to 9 years.
OL,12,FSarah Murphy, Minister for Mental
OL,13,FHealth and Wellbeing, said, "Women
OL,14,Fhave told us that they feel they are
OL,15,Fnot heard, and their symptoms are
OL,16,Fignored.
OL,18,F"This training ensures women's voices
OL,19,Fare central to their healthcare
OL,20,Fexperience, and it helps GPs support
OL,21,Ftheir patients more effectively."
