OL,6,FWhat is endometriosis?
OL,8,FIt's caused when tissue similar to the
OL,9,Flining of the womb starts to grow
OL,10,Felsewhere.
OL,12,FEach month, cells react in the same
OL,13,Fway as those in the womb, building up
OL,14,Fand then breaking down and bleeding.
OL,16,FBut unlike cells in the womb that
OL,17,Fleave the body as a period, this blood
OL,18,Fhas nowhere to go and can't escape the
OL,19,Fbody.
