OL,6,FThe new expert-led training will be
OL,7,Frolled out across Wales and, among
OL,8,Fthose already participating, has led
OL,9,Fto a 43% increase in GPs' knowledge of
OL,10,Fthe condition.
OL,12,FDr Mirka Slavska is one of the
OL,13,Fspecialist consultants who has
OL,14,Fdelivered the training. She said,
OL,15,F""The session covered differential
OL,16,Fdiagnoses, referral pathways, novel
OL,17,Fdiagnostic and treatment options, and
OL,18,Fintroduced the Endometriosis Cymru
OL,19,Fsymptom reporting tool.
